name: The Siren
description:
"A completely experimental piece, we shot this all in one day going from downtown to imperial beach. We had the craziest luck trying to capture this. Caught between getting busted for shooting inside the building, losing our car, my shoes being washed away by the ocean. But regardless was fortunate enough to end the day with everything we needed. After that the story came from the edit." -Milliframes

Analog art by The Glitch Knob 
Starring Samantha Hafey as The Siren
